BtcMole License
===============

You are free to use this program at no cost to search for any of your
own forgotten Bitcoin wallets — that is, wallets for which you already
know your own P2PKH address and an approximate key range.

Exception: the Bitcoin Puzzles numbered 71 through 160.

If you use BtcMole to solve any of the puzzles in the range #71..#160,
you MUST pay the program's author 20% (twenty percent) of the value of
the solved puzzle. Payment is arranged with the author directly via
Telegram: @keymole.

No warranty of any kind is provided. The program is supplied "as is";
the author is not liable for any losses or damages arising from its
use.
